{"tid":1187951,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"核事故劇集輕鬆擊敗《權力的遊戲》 引發網民激烈討論我國實情","createTime":"2019-06-06T03:22:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-06T16:21:06.000Z","uid":250639,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"388b7f49adca3fbd4d9fd4734b72e423174c8c94","tid":1187951,"uid":250639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T03:22:11.000Z","msg":"為什麼核災難輕鬆擊敗《權力的遊戲》？前蘇聯究竟隱瞞了什麼秘密 切爾諾貝利01<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3T98ybIu6gE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3T98ybIu6gE&d=HGsIALD6rBmJFWdd%2FklElsVJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=5fc2e36f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3T98ybIu6gE</a><br />\n<br />\n切爾諾貝利核事故，是人類史上最嚴重的核輻射洩漏事故，究竟為什麼一部只有五集的迷你劇會比《權力的遊戲》更火熱呢？<br />\n<br />\n《切爾諾貝爾》長期堅守在某最大美劇發佈網的第一，更是秒殺了《權力的遊戲》最終季（當然爛尾不是主因），長期榮登榜首呢，原因之一是完美演繹了史無人知的過程，細緻演繹了人性的弱點。<br />\n<br />\n還有，就是各方網友激烈辯論上國、中國、下國、某國對災難的處理方法，從而討論各國民族的傳統，還有更多的根本性問題。<br />\n<br />\n除了欣賞劇集，從中思考，更要吃著花生看評論。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zKNd9ak.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzKNd9ak.png&h=211ffabc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c0ad8f2b9b9458dca1b1348713cddb397f4913e2","tid":1187951,"uid":228328,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T03:27:44.000Z","msg":"我都想睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd3ec49e15197fb211d2ecd0f82093a765f2cb43","tid":1187951,"uid":125724,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T03:30:13.000Z","msg":"係幾好睇，可能因為短所以劇情好緊湊"},{"pid":"4a12b4150413c9789909f97fab78c3f9dde71090","tid":1187951,"uid":55913,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T03:46:39.000Z","msg":"支那日日都爆啦 慣左"},{"pid":"5e3cdc5ccb94fa37ac702ee63bb1535db1419517","tid":1187951,"uid":61281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T03:49:34.000Z","msg":"實戰救港<br />\n<br />\n[69兵法] 排陣+策略 *習近平權鬥*<br />\n<br 